{
  "stem": "311.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was back in Cracow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I see Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Gross, who-- well, you can blame now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He got 20 years, you know, seeing him with a-- schlepping from one jail to the other-- food for the-- from one criminal to the other, through the main streets.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'45.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'45, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At Schindler, we went '44.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then May-- in May 8th, at-- the day the war ended, this is it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Russians.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At first you know, it-- it-- it's amazing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There comes a little kid, you know, maybe-- maybe-- he looked like 12, maybe he was 15, on a horse, naked.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Naked horse, nothing on him, just the-- the-- the mouthpiece, you know, to hold him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He comes in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He stands up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he gives-- he-- he has a whole speech.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, he was one they send out before anybody comes in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he gives on a whole speech.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Russian, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you know, most of the guys, you know, when you know Polish, Russian, ain't so-- it's-- it's a-- it's easy to understand.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The whole German damn thing, they run away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And here, look who's coming?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who they worrying about?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then comes in, about 11 o'clock in the afternoon, then comes the-- they came in, with a-- the trucks, the Russian trucks came in.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So-- but they came light.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They came with a radio, with the operators.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, there was a Russian-Jewish girl there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was operating the-- the telephones and everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Schindler, there was the boys already took him out from the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our fellows, you know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish boys, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was Orbach was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
